--- title: "Critical Result Callback Monitor" output: flexdashboard::flex_dashboard: orientation: rows vertical_layout: fill --- Overall {data-icon="fa-phone-volume"} ============================= Row -------------------------------------- ### Mean callback time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/avg-tat_3afe71ad360f05a4a80e305dbd507955'} ```{.r .cell-code} mean_tat <- round(mean(cb_data$call_tat), 0) valueBox(value = mean_tat, icon = "fa-stopwatch", caption = "Mean callback time", color = "#708090") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 15 ``` ::: ::: ### Total calls ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/total-calls_bbe638f31a8d812a71a55777d33493c9'} ```{.r .cell-code} calls <- cb_data %>% nrow() valueBox(value = calls, icon = "fa-hashtag", caption = "Total calls", color = "orange") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 2167 ``` ::: ::: ### Percent on Time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/pct-on-time_89891de91e46436f220c659383976b66'} ```{.r .cell-code} ontime_n <- cb_data %>% filter(call_tat <= 30) %>% nrow() late_n <- cb_data %>% filter(call_tat >30) %>% nrow() pct_ontime <- round((ontime_n/calls)*100,0) if(pct_ontime >= 95){ valueBox(value = pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "mediumseagreen") #3CB371 } else{ valueBox(value = pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "indianred")} #CD5C5C ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 89 ``` ::: ::: Row ---------------------------------- ### Weekly Overview: Hourly Call Breakdown for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/plot-hourly-by-day-no-weekend_cdf273a3a92573ca631a97f0d22d92c7'} ```{.r .cell-code} p1 <- ggplot(filter(cb_data, call_wday %in% c("Mon", "Tue", "Wed", "Thu", "Fri"))) + geom_bar(aes(x = call_hour, fill = tech_location)) + facet_grid(call_wday~call_week) + labs(x = "Hour", y = "Count", fill = "Type") + scale_fill_manual(values=c("steelblue3", "gray60")) + theme_bw() + theme(legend.position = "top") ggplotly(p1) %>% layout(legend = list(orientation = "h", x = 0.35, y = 1.2)) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} # have to manually position the legend ``` ::: ### Daily Call Volumes for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/plot-daily-volumes_8a8bcfdc6a946f046f0a95000449eabf'} ```{.r .cell-code} daily_vol <- cb_data %>% group_by(call_year, call_month, call_date) %>% summarize(n = n()) %>% ungroup() %>% unite(dttm, call_year, call_month, call_date, sep = "-", remove = TRUE) %>% mutate(dttm = as.Date(dttm)) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` `summarise()` has grouped output by 'call_year', 'call_month'. You can override using the `.groups` argument. ``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} #dygraph requires ts object daily_vol_ts <- xts(daily_vol$n, order.by = daily_vol$dttm) p2 <- dygraph(daily_vol_ts) %>% dyOptions(colors = "#4F94CD", strokeWidth = 2) p2 ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: Call Center {data-icon="fa-users"} ============================= Row -------------------------------------- ### Mean callback time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/avg-tat-cc_50149b21f2bd12a53e2dfadde22293fb'} ```{.r .cell-code} cc_calls <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "CallCenter") mean_tat_cc <- round(mean(cc_calls$call_tat),0) valueBox(value = mean_tat_cc, icon = "fa-stopwatch", caption = "Mean callback time", color = "#708090") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 10 ``` ::: ::: ### Total calls ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/total-calls-cc_170f0afc178a2e295ed1557568a3a12a'} ```{.r .cell-code} cc_calls_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "CallCenter") %>% nrow() valueBox(value = cc_calls_n, icon = "fa-hashtag", caption = "Total calls", color = "orange") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 864 ``` ::: ::: ### Percent on Time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/pct-on-time-cc_3c0f94c15b4423220e7ae0b506fb5e2d'} ```{.r .cell-code} cc_ontime_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "CallCenter", call_tat <= 30) %>% nrow() cc_late_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "CallCenter", call_tat >30) %>% nrow() cc_pct_ontime <- round((cc_ontime_n/cc_calls_n)*100,0) if(cc_pct_ontime >= 95){ valueBox(value = cc_pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "mediumseagreen") #3CB371 } else{ valueBox(value = cc_pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "indianred")} #CD5C5C ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 99 ``` ::: ::: Row -------------------------------------- ### Overdue Call Details for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/cc-overdue_24ec9771851216214656f9392c7afdb8'} ```{.r .cell-code} cc_late <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "CallCenter", call_tat >30) %>% select(call_tat, accession, pt_type, pt_loc_code, test_code, result_datetime, phoned_title, tech) datatable(cc_late, options = list(pageLength = 20, autoWidth = TRUE)) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Tech Summary for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/cc-tech_cdc1f9af721d3d20c3401fb3811fd265'} ```{.r .cell-code} p3 <- hcboxplot( outliers = FALSE, x = cc_calls$call_tat, var = cc_calls$tech, name = "TAT", color = "#4F94CD", lineWidth = 2) %>% hc_title(text = "") %>% hc_xAxis(title = list(text = "Tech Code")) %>% hc_yAxis(title = list(text = "Call Time in Min")) %>% hc_chart(type = "column") ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` Warning: 'hcboxplot' is deprecated. Use 'data_to_boxplot' instead. See help("Deprecated") ``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} p3 ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: Non Call Center {data-icon="fa-users"} ============================= Row -------------------------------------- ### Mean callback time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/avg-tat-non_baaceced75f1ae5500fcc4feb58bfdcc'} ```{.r .cell-code} non_calls <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "Non-CC") mean_tat_non <- round(mean(non_calls$call_tat),0) valueBox(value = mean_tat_non, icon = "fa-stopwatch", caption = "Mean callback time", color = "#708090") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 18 ``` ::: ::: ### Total calls ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/total-calls-non_11770ab79e4190add88282d5951deed7'} ```{.r .cell-code} non_calls_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "Non-CC") %>% nrow() valueBox(value = non_calls_n, icon = "fa-hashtag", caption = "Total calls", color = "orange") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 1303 ``` ::: ::: ### Percent on Time ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/pct-on-time-non_6d361861c8292355cc4fa59b91a76973'} ```{.r .cell-code} non_ontime_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "Non-CC", call_tat <= 30) %>% nrow() non_late_n <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "Non-CC", call_tat >30) %>% nrow() non_pct_ontime <- round((non_ontime_n/non_calls_n)*100,0) if(non_pct_ontime >= 95){ valueBox(value = non_pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "mediumseagreen") #3CB371 } else{ valueBox(value = non_pct_ontime, icon = "fa-percent", caption = "Percent on time", color = "indianred")} #CD5C5C ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html} 82 ``` ::: ::: Row -------------------------------------- ### Overdue Call Details for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/non-overdue_08fef0b90dad1975436ef1a248d59b4c'} ```{.r .cell-code} non_late <- cb_data %>% filter(tech_location == "Non-CC", call_tat >30) %>% select(call_tat, accession, pt_type, pt_loc_code, test_code, result_datetime, phoned_title, tech) datatable(non_late, options = list(pageLength = 20, autoWidth = TRUE)) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Tech Summary for 2020-07-01 through 2020-07-31 ::: {.cell hash='example_cache/html/non-tech_b2ccd8a8fef1d83de33da7fb91d6c5d5'} ```{.r .cell-code} p4 <- hcboxplot( outliers = FALSE, x = non_calls$call_tat, var = non_calls$tech, name = "TAT", color = "#4F94CD", lineWidth = 2) %>% hc_title(text = "") %>% hc_xAxis(title = list(text = "Tech Code")) %>% hc_yAxis(title = list(text = "Call Time in Min")) %>% hc_chart(type = "column") ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` Warning: 'hcboxplot' is deprecated. Use 'data_to_boxplot' instead. See help("Deprecated") ``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} p4 ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: :::
